    "description": "<p>YIXIN PRECISION ENGINEERING PTE LTD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>About Us<br>\nYixin Precision is a vibrant company which was established in 1995 and incorporated as a private company in 2001.<br>\n<br>\nWe provide services in mold making, plastic injection molding and assembly. Mold making include specialty mold for metal injection molding (MIM) and die casting molds. The end molded components could be use for disposable medical devices or microfluidics chips.</p>",
